>>title:Szechwan Dipping Sauce
>>description: Spicy Chinese dipping sauce for dumplings 
>>tags: chinese, sauce, dumplings
Mix @chopped ginger{1%tbsp} @chopped garlic{1%tbsp} @soy sauce{2%tbsp} @black vinegar{1%tbsp} , @sichuan peppercorns{1%tsp} , @shaoxing wine{1%tbsp} , @sugar{1%tsp} @white pepper{1/2%tsp} @chopped scallions{1%tbsp} @chili oil{2%tbsp} 

Serve as a dipping sauce for dumplings or spring rolls.